            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "澳洲3月就業增長放緩;失業率穩定在4.3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/URRsuqDo3TnZqUdih_ooHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED6H07K_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 官方數據週四顯示,澳洲3月失業率保持穩定,而就業增長較上月放緩,顯示勞動市場仍具韌性但正在降溫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲統計局表示,就業人數在3月增加17,900人,低於2月強勁的48,900人增幅,但大致符合19,100人的預期增幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">失業率維持在4.3%不變,符合預期,而勞動參與率則從上月的66.9%小幅下降至66.8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">就業增長主要由全職就業推動,全職職位激增52,500個,抵消了約30,500個兼職職位的下降。向全職工作的轉變顯示,儘管招聘動能有所降溫,但勞動力需求仍具潛在實力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d4a7e763-6b3b-3d8f-8a7b-110568f5cdbb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">失業人數略有下降,而總工作時數月增0.5%,顯示勞動力產能持續被利用。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,整體就業增長放緩以及勞動參與率下降,可能預示著就業狀況開始放鬆的早期跡象,政策制定者將密切關注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些數據公布之際,澳洲儲備銀行仍專注於通脹風險。該央行今年已兩次加息至4.1%,並表示不確定當前的政策設定是否足以將通脹率拉回2-3%的目標區間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Capital Economics分析師在報告中表示:\"誠然,勞動市場是經濟活動的下游指標,可能需要一段時間才會出現裂痕。然而,由於澳洲儲備銀行判斷就業水平高於其最大可持續水平,一些放鬆可能會受到歡迎。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師寫道:\"對央行而言,更緊迫的擔憂將是持續飆升的價格壓力。\"他們補充說,預計澳洲儲備銀行將再加息兩次,每次25個基點,使現金利率在第三季度達到4.60%的峰值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳元兌AUD/USD週四上漲0.2%。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B23%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7%E6%94%BE%E7%B7%A9-%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%A84-3-025103660.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 11:10:09",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
